002package com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.payment;
003
004import java.util.function.Function;
005
006import com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.*;
007
008public class TransactionQueryBuilderDsl {
009    public TransactionQueryBuilderDsl() {
010    }
011
012    public static TransactionQueryBuilderDsl of() {
013        return new TransactionQueryBuilderDsl();
014    }
015
016    public StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<TransactionQueryBuilderDsl> id() {
017        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("id")),
018            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, TransactionQueryBuilderDsl::of));
019    }
020
021    public DateTimeComparisonPredicateBuilder<TransactionQueryBuilderDsl> timestamp() {
022        return new DateTimeComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
023            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("timestamp")),
024            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, TransactionQueryBuilderDsl::of));
025    }
026
027    public StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<TransactionQueryBuilderDsl> type() {
028        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
029            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("type")),
030            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, TransactionQueryBuilderDsl::of));
031    }
032
033    public CombinationQueryPredicate<TransactionQueryBuilderDsl> amount(
034            Function<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.CentPrecisionMoneyQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.CentPrecisionMoneyQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
035        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
036                .parent(ConstantQueryPredicate.of().constant("amount"))
037                .inner(fn.apply(com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.common.CentPrecisionMoneyQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
038            TransactionQueryBuilderDsl::of);
039    }
040
041    public StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<TransactionQueryBuilderDsl> interactionId() {
042        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
043            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("interactionId")),
044            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, TransactionQueryBuilderDsl::of));
045    }
046
047    public StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<TransactionQueryBuilderDsl> state() {
048        return new StringComparisonPredicateBuilder<>(
049            BinaryQueryPredicate.of().left(new ConstantQueryPredicate("state")),
050            p -> new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(p, TransactionQueryBuilderDsl::of));
051    }
052
053    public CombinationQueryPredicate<TransactionQueryBuilderDsl> custom(
054            Function<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.type.CustomFieldsQueryBuilderDsl, CombinationQueryPredicate<com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.type.CustomFieldsQueryBuilderDsl>> fn) {
055        return new CombinationQueryPredicate<>(
056            ContainerQueryPredicate.of()
057                    .parent(ConstantQueryPredicate.of().constant("custom"))
058                    .inner(fn.apply(com.commercetools.api.predicates.query.type.CustomFieldsQueryBuilderDsl.of())),
059            TransactionQueryBuilderDsl::of);
060    }
061
062}
